ygData.messageBody:
I myself do not do the power-leveling thing. It's
my friend that does it for money. As far as I know
he only does it on the Brell server because that's
where his level 50 Druid is.<br><br>He gets the account
info. He gives the login to another friend of his. That
guy logs on as the level 1 guy. My original friend
logs on as his level 50 Druid and procedes to
power-level the new account. When finished, he gets
paid.<br><br>Nelmunbar<br>Enchanter on Brell
